[FLsnow&KeyFC][Kanon][BDRIP][1080p][CHS_CHT_JPN_ENG][H.264/AVC 10bpp]

In celebration of Naoki Hisaya's new stuff, Sora no Method, FLsnow & KeyFC bring you with the impressive work of Kanon (2006).

The English subtitles are embedded but not set as default. You can either set your player to prefer English subtitle tracks, or choose the English subs manually.

AVC version of this release requires decoders, splitters or players that support H.264/AVC High10 Profile (ISO/IEC 14496-10:2005), FLAC, Matroska and BD-PGS subtitle formats. For Windows users, we recommend MPC-HC.


Some pictures are encoded in WebP-Lossless format. You can open these files with XnView, XnViewMP and IrfanView; or you can install WebP Codec for Windows and open them with any software that uses WIC (e.g. Windows Photo Viewer).
